FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Everything you need to know about our gym management app
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_1: What features does the app offer?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Our app provides a comprehensive suite of tools to streamline gym operations. From member management to class scheduling, billing to inventory tracking, we've got you covered.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_2: How does the app help with member management?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: Easily manage member information, track attendance, and send automated reminders for renewals and payments. Our app keeps your member database organized and up-to-date.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: Can I manage class schedules and instructor assignments?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: Absolutely! Create and publish class schedules, assign instructors, and allow members to book classes directly through the app. Stay on top of your programming with ease.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: How does billing and payments work?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Streamline your billing process with automated membership fees, class packages, and one-time payments. Members can securely store payment info and renew with just a tap.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_5: Can I track inventory and place orders?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: Yes, our inventory management tools let you monitor stock levels, receive low-stock alerts, and place orders with partnered suppliers. Never run out of essentials again.

ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: GymBuilder is a comprehensive app designed to help you build and maintain a successful gym or fitness center. It provides tools for managing memberships, scheduling classes, tracking workouts, and more.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_2: How does GymBuilder help with member management?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: GymBuilder streamlines member management by providing a centralized database for storing member information, tracking payments, and monitoring attendance. You can easily add new members, update their profiles, and communicate with them through the app.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_3: Can GymBuilder help with class scheduling?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Absolutely! GymBuilder comes with a powerful class scheduling feature that allows you to create and manage various fitness classes, assign instructors, and enable members to sign up conveniently.
ACCORDION_QUESTION_4: Does GymBuilder integrate with fitness tracking devices?
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: Yes, GymBuilder can integrate with popular fitness tracking devices and apps, allowing members to seamlessly sync their workout data and progress. This enables you to provide personalized coaching and monitor their overall fitness journey.
PAGE_DETAIL_1_VALUE: Our app provides personalized workout plans and nutrition guidance to help you achieve your fitness goals, whether it's building muscle, losing weight, or improving overall health.
PAGE_DETAIL_2_VALUE: Stay motivated by monitoring your workouts, body measurements, and macronutrient intake within the app. Visual representations of your progress will keep you inspired.
PAGE_DETAIL_3_VALUE: Get access to a wealth of knowledge from certified personal trainers and nutritionists who will provide tips, answer your questions, and ensure you're on the right path.
